import React from 'react'
import { Col, Container, Row } from 'react-bootstrap'

const Dashboard = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <Section>
        <Container>
            <Row>
                <Col md={3}>


                </Col>
                <Col md={9} ></Col>
            </Row>
        </Container>
    </Section>
    </>
  )
}

export default Dashboard
